{
  "stem": "27335.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When you come, come to harvest, you come to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then-- then-- he was the-- he was the, uh, uh, Labor Office, who supplies the farmers with the harvest labors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the prairie farms out-- out there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You see there's this-- you know, prairies, it's like [INAUDIBLE] Alberta-- the smallest farm was a half section, which means it's 120 acres.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he sent us to a-- to a farm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And between the two of us, in the harvest and threshing time, we made a whole sum of $126.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That was a big [INAUDIBLE] in my day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, that was the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] really deep, in [INAUDIBLE] of the Depression.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the-- well, we settled on that-- on that farm there, and built-- well, there-- there were people with-- in-- in Leduc-- it was 20 miles away-- away from the place where we-- and there were some Hungarians there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a Hungarian-- a Hungarian blacksmith, and there was a Hungarian-- Hungarian shoemaker, in that region, in Leduc.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, you should remember, Leduc was the first place where the oil came out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to work on a farm-- [LAUGHS] start the first-- the first oil.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that blacksmith had a-- had a quarter section of land out there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, he could afford it-- what would mind you-- afford a section of $4,600-- [INAUDIBLE] 160 acres land.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And through him, well, we, uh, got acquainted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then aligning in-- into Edmonton.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so on in Edmonton, I was Hungarian community, already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, we worked in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we then-- when people found out in Edmonton-- mind you, leftist people-- [LAUGHS] found out, they came to visit us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was a shoemaker, the other-- other-- what-- what-- what was he?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
